{{Soviet Union sidebar}}
The '''Supreme Court of the Soviet Union''' ({{lang-ru|Верховный Суд СССР}}) was the highest court of the [[Soviet Union]] during its existence. The Supreme Court of the USSR included a [[Military Collegium of the Supreme Court of the Soviet Union|Military Collegium]] and other elements which were not typical of supreme courts found in other countries, then or now.

